com.kuka.geometry

Class Tool

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kuka.geometry.SpatialObject
      • com.kuka.geometry.PhysicalObject
        • com.kuka.geometry.Tool
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICapabilityContainer, IMovable, IMovableObject

    public class Tool
extends PhysicalObject
    A class used to mark objects that are used as tools in applications.

    A Tool is a subclass of a PhysicalObject. It does not offer any additional functionality. Its usage is merely to mark the tool objects.
